(491, 91, '_form', '<div id=\"personal-information\">\n<h3>Personal Information</h3>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Date: <br />[date date]</div>\n<div style=\"display:none\" class=\"span6\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\"><p>Name *:<br /> [text* your-name]</p></div>\n<div class=\"span6\">Social Security No.:<br />[text social-security-no]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\"><p>Present Address:<br />[text present-address]</p></div>\n<div class=\"span6\"><p>Permanent Address:<br />[text permanent-address]</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Phone Number:<br />[number phone-number]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">Referred by:<br />[text referred-by]</div>\n</div>\n<p>Email *:<br />[email* your-email]</p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n\n<div id=\"employment-desired\">\n<h3>Employment Desired</h3>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span4\">Position:<br />[text position]</div>\n<div class=\"span4\">Date Available:<br />[date date-available]</div>\n<div class=\"span4\">Salary Req.:<br />[text salary-req]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Are you employed:<br />[select are-you-employed \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">If so, may we inquire of your present employer?:<br />[select inquireofyourpresentemployer \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span4\">Ever applied to this company?:<br />[select Everappliedtothiscompany \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"span4\">Where?:<br />[text Where]</div>\n<div class=\"span4\">When?:<br />[date When]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<hr />\n\n<div id=\"education\">\n<h3>Education</h3>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\"> &nbsp; </div>\n<div class=\"span3\">Name &amp; School Location</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">*Years Attended</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">*Date Graduated</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">Area of Study</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">Grammar School</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[textarea education-details-grammar-school 40x2]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[date* education-years-attended-grammar-school]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[date* education-date-graduated-grammar-school]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[text education-area-of-study-grammar-school]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">High School</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[textarea education-details-high-school 40x2]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[date* education-years-attended-high-school]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[date* education-date-graduated-high-school]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[text education-area-of-study-high-school]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">College</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[textarea education-details-college 40x2]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[date* education-years-attended-college]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[date* education-date-graduated-college]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[text education-area-of-study-college]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">Trade, Business or Correspond. School</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[textarea education-details-trade-business-correspond-school 40x2]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[date* education-years-attended-trade-business-correspond-school]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[date* education-date-graduated-trade-business-correspond-school]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[text education-area-of-study-trade-business-correspond-school]</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<hr />\n\n<div id=\"general\">\n<h3>General</h3>\n<p>Subjects of Special Study or Research Work?<br />[text SubjectsofSpecialStudyorResearchWork]</p>\n<p>What foreign languages do you speak fluently?<br />[text Whatforeignlanguagesdoyouspeakfluently]</p> \n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Read:<br />[text read]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">Write:<br />[text write]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">U.S. Military Service:<br />[text U.S.MilitaryService]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">Rank:<br />[text rank]</div>\n</div>\n<p>Member of National Guard/Reserves?<br />[text MemberofNationalGuardReserves]</p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n\n<div id=\"habre-special-questions\">\n<h3>Special Questions</h3>\n<p>Do not answer <b>any</b> of the questions in this framed area unless the employer has <b>checked a box preceding</b> a question, thereby indicating that the information is required for a bona fide occupational qualification, is dictated by National Security Laws, or is needed for other legally permissible reasons.</p>\n<div id=\"special-questions\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">Height:<br />[text height]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">Feet:<br />[text feet]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">Inches:<br />[text inches]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">Other:<br />[text other]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Weight:<br />[text weight]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">lbs:<br />[text lbs]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">U.S. Citizen:<br />[select U.S.Citizen \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">US Naturalization Number:<br />[text USNaturalizationNumber]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Date of Birth**:<br />[date* DateofBirth]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">Are you Permanent Resident:<br />[select AreyouPermanentResident \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Place of Birth**:<br />[text* PlaceofBirth]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">INS A Number:<br />[text INSANumber]</div>\n<p>** The Age Discrimination Act of 1967 prohibits discrimination on the basis of age with respect to individiuals who are at least 40 but less than 70 years of age.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<hr />\n\n<div id=\"physical-record\">\n<h3>Physical Record</h3>\n<p>Do you have any physical defects that prejudice that preclude you from performing any work for which you are being considered?<br />[select Doyouhaveanyphysicaldefectsthatprejudicethatprecludeyoufromperforminganyworkforwhichyouarebeingconsidered \"Yes\" \"No\"]</p>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Were you ever injured?<br />[select Wereyoueverinjured \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">Give Details:<br />[text GiveDetails]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span4\">Have you any defects in hearing?<br />[select Haveyouanydefectsinhearing \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"span4\">In vision?<br />[select Invision \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n<div class=\"span4\">In speech?<br />[select Inspeech \"Yes\" \"No\"]</div>\n</div>\n<p>In case of emergency, notify:<br />[text Incaseofemergencynotify] </p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n\n<div id=\"former-employers\">\n<h3>Former Employers</h3>\n<p>(List below your last four employers, starting with the most recent one first.)</p>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">Date (M/Y)</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">Name, Address& Phone of Employer</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">Salary</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">Position</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">Reason Left</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">From <br /> [date former-employers-from-date-1]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">To <br /> [date former-employers-to-date-1]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[textarea former-employers-details-1 40x2]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[text former-employers-salary-1]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[text former-employers-position-1]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[textarea former-employers-reason-left-1 40x2]</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">From <br /> [date former-employers-from-date-2 40x2]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">To <br /> [date former-employers-to-date-2]</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[textarea former-employers-details-2 40x2]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[text former-employers-salary-2]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[text former-employers-position-2]</div>\n<div class=\"span2\">[textarea former-employers-reason-left-2 40x2]</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<hr />\n\n<div id=\"references\">\n<h3>References</h3>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">Name</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">Address &amp; Phone</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">Business</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">Years Known</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesname1]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesaddress1]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesbusiness1]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesyearsknown1]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesname2]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesaddress2]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesbusiness2]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesyearsknown2]</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesname3]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesaddress3]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesbusiness3]</div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text referencesyearsknown3]</div>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n<hr />\n\n<div id=\"remarks\">\n<h3>Remarks</h3>\n<p>To be filled by Eco-Friendly Lawn and Landscaping, LLC</p>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Appearance:<br />[text appearance]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">Character:<br />[text character]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Personality:<br />[text personality]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">Ability:<br />[text ability]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span4\">Hired:<br />[text hired]</div>\n<div class=\"span4\">For Dept:<br />[text for-dept]</div>\n<div class=\"span4\">Position:<br />[text position]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Will Report:<br />[text will-report]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">Salary/Wages:<br />[text salary-wages]</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span3\">Approved:<br /></div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text approved-1]<br /></div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text approved-2]<br /></div>\n<div class=\"span3\">[text approved-3]<br /></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"row-fluid\">\n<div class=\"span6\">Employment Manager:<br />[text employment-manager]</div>\n<div class=\"span6\">Dept. Head:<br />[text dept-head]</div>\n</div>\n<p>General Manager:<br />[text general-manager]</p>\n</div>\n<hr />\n\n<p>This form has been designed to comply with State and Federal Fair Employment Practice laws prohibiting discrimination on the basis of an applicant’s sex or minority status. Questions directly or indirectly reflecting such status have been included only where needed to determine a bona fide occupational qualification or for other permissible purposes. Such questions are appropriately noted on the application. Notwithstanding these efforts, the manufacturer of this form assumes no responsibility , and hereby disclaims any liability for inclusion in this form, of any questions upon which a violation of State and Federal Fair Employment Practice laws may be based.</p>\n<hr />\n\n<p>Please verify below that you are Human\n[recaptcha]</p>\n<p>[submit \"Send\"]</p>\n\n<p>*=Required</p>'),
