sofSpecialStudyorResearchWork]\nWhat foreign languages do you speak fluently?:[Whatforeignlanguagesdoyouspeakfluently]\nRead:[read]\nWrite:[write]\nU.S. Military Service:[U.S.MilitaryService]\nRank:[rank]\nMember of National Guard/Reserves?:[MemberofNationalGuardReserves]\n\n\nSpecial Questions\nHeight: [height]\nFeet: [feet]\nInches: [inches]\nOther: [other]\nWeight: [weight]\nlbs: [lbs]\nU.S. Citizen: [U.S.Citizen]\nUS Naturalization Number: [USNaturalizationNumber]\nDate of Birth: [DateofBirth]\nAre you Permanent Resident: [AreyouPermanentResident]\nPlace of Birth: [PlaceofBirth]\nINS A Number: [INSANumber]\n\n\nPhysical Record\nDo you have any physical defects that prejudice that preclude you from performing any work for which you are being considered?\n[Doyouhaveanyphysicaldefectsthatprejudicethatprecludeyoufromperforminganyworkforwhichyouarebeingconsidered]\nWere you ever injured? [Wereyoueverinjured]\nGive Details: [GiveDetails]\nHave you any defects in hearing? [Haveyouanydefectsinhearing]\nIn vision? [Invision]\nIn speech? [Inspeech]\nIn case of emergency, notify: [Incaseofemergencynotify]\n\n\nFormer Employers\nFrom: [former-employers-from-date-1]\nTo: [former-employers-to-date-1]\nName, Address& Phone of Employer: [former-employers-details-1]\nSalary: [former-employers-salary-1]\nPosition: [former-employers-position-1]\nReason Left: [former-employers-reason-left-1]\nFrom: [former-employers-from-date-2]\nTo: [former-employers-to-date-2]\nName, Address& Phone of Employer: [former-employers-details-2]\nSalary: [former-employers-salary-2]\nPosition: [former-employers-position-2]\nReason Left: [former-employers-reason-left-2]\n\n\nReferences\nName: [referencesname1]\nAddress & Phone: [referencesaddress1]\nBusiness: [referencesbusiness1]\nYears Known: [referencesyearsknown1]\nName: [referencesname2]\nAddress & Phone: [referencesaddress2]\nBusiness: [referencesbusiness2]\nYears Known: [referencesyearsknown2]\nName: [referencesname3]\nAddress & Phone: [references