(135, 1, '2015-03-01 13:51:13', '2015-03-01 13:51:13', '\"Prompt replly to inspect grounds and offer specific date. Veru puntual, efficient and courteous. Absolutley fantastaic work in clearing lawn/leaves. Will definelty call them back with the next wind storm. the very best, fair and economical.\" (Homeadvisor)\n\nBurke VA 22915\n\nHomeadvisor Member', 'Paul Fedio', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'paul-fedio', '', '', '2015-03-01 13:51:13', '2015-03-01 13:51:13', '', 0, 'http://ecollc.dev/?p=135', 0, 'post', '', 0),
