(531, 1, '2016-06-25 04:35:16', '2016-06-25 04:35:16', '<blockquote>Eco-friendly provided services for the lawn at my previous address, with remarkable results. He was one of my first calls when I bought my new home. Mahesh and his team are true professionals who know what they are doing. The prices for the quality of service and time they invest are extremely reasonable. I would highly recommend Eco-friendly lawn services.\r\n\r\nDeAnn Farr</blockquote>\r\n[gallery link=\"file\" ids=\"687,875,876,877,878,879,880\"]', 'Lawn Care', 'Eco-friendly provided services for the lawn at my previous address, with remarkable results. He was one of my first calls when I bought my new home. Mahesh and his team are true professionals who know what they are doing. -DeAnn Farr', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'lawn-care', '', '', '2016-08-04 20:57:18', '2016-08-04 20:57:18', '', 0, 'http://dev.habrenepal.com.np/?p=531', 0, 'post', '', 0);
