(637, 1, '2016-07-03 10:33:28', '2016-07-03 10:33:28', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-621\" src=\"http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Lawn-Bed-Care.jpg\" alt=\"Lawn/Bed Care\" width=\"870\" height=\"280\" />\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n<h2>We predominantly cater:</h2>\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Detox Eden Program (A Comprehensive Organic Program)\r\nThis program caters a long-term engagement with our clients to revive the natural splendor of lawn/bed deteriorated by inorganic treatment or maintenance. We discuss our clients and explore collaborative possibilities about the range of services we cater and beyond.</li>\r\n 	<li>Verdant Eden program (Complete Organic)\r\nThis program is complete organic program basically focused on providing complete organic solutions to our clients. This program can be, with the consent of our clients, upgraded to the \"Detox Eden Program\".</li>\r\n 	<li>Healthy Eden Program (Half-organic)\r\nThis program is for our clients who prefer chemicals to organic treatment. Although we encourage adopting organic solutions, we provide this service using minimal of chemicals and as per the set standards.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\nPlease see <a href=\"http://dev.habrenepal.com.np/faq/\">FAQ\'s</a> about Organic program.\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\n[gallery link=\"file\" ids=\"631,632,633,634,635,636\"]', 'Lawn/Bed Care', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '30-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:33:28', '2016-07-03 10:33:28', '', 30, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/30-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(638, 1, '2016-07-03 10:38:04', '2016-07-03 10:38:04', '', 'Landscape Maintenance', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'landscape-maintenance', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:38:11', '2016-07-03 10:38:11', '', 31, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Landscape-Maintenance.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(639, 1, '2016-07-03 10:38:22', '2016-07-03 10:38:22', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-638\" src=\"http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Landscape-Maintenance.jpg\" alt=\"Landscape Maintenance\" width=\"870\" height=\"280\" />\n\n<hr />\n\nWe also provide regular and seasonal landscaping services like : regular lawn mowing &amp; edging, pruning of all ornamental plants, hand weeding, aerating and over-seeding, mulching, fertilizing, leaf removal and pre—season clean up.', 'Landscape Maintenance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '31-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:38:22', '2016-07-03 10:38:22', '', 31, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/31-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(640, 1, '2016-07-03 10:38:27', '2016-07-03 10:38:27', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-638\" src=\"http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/Landscape-Maintenance.jpg\" alt=\"Landscape Maintenance\" width=\"870\" height=\"280\" />\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nWe also provide regular and seasonal landscaping services like : regular lawn mowing &amp; edging, pruning of all ornamental plants, hand weeding, aerating and over-seeding, mulching, fertilizing, leaf removal and pre—season clean up.', 'Landscape Maintenance', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '31-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:38:27', '2016-07-03 10:38:27', '', 31, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/31-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(641, 1, '2016-07-03 10:39:19', '2016-07-03 10:39:19', '', 'Landscape Design', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'landscape-design-2', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:39:28', '2016-07-03 10:39:28', '', 436, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Landscape-Design.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(642, 1, '2016-07-03 10:39:42', '2016-07-03 10:39:42', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-641\" src=\"http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Landscape-Design.jpg\" alt=\"Landscape Design\" width=\"870\" height=\"280\" />\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nAs per you needs and size of your property, we execute ingenious hardscaping and innovative finishing touches. Our services include, but not limited to:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Start up front</li>\r\n 	<li>Befitting plants at appropriate places (Texture/Shape)</li>\r\n 	<li>Outdoor lightening ideas and designs</li>\r\n 	<li>Hardscaping (Sidewalk, walkaway, patio, driveway, parking areas, side yards and dog\'s run and arbor)</li>\r\n 	<li>Options to Grass/Patches (Special plants like Creeping speedwell, Roman Chamomile, Irish Moss etc. as an alternative to grass)</li>\r\n 	<li>Brushstrokes ( artifacts, containers, window boxes, water features, (hanging) baskets, statues as per personal taste of our clients)</li>\r\n 	<li>Regular Maintenance</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong><em>We also help our clients to design their landscape as per the ancient wisdom of Indian Vastu Shastra &amp; Chinese Feng Shui for good luck, positive vibrations and prosperity. </em></strong>', 'Landscape Design', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '436-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:39:42', '2016-07-03 10:39:42', '', 436, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/436-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(643, 1, '2016-07-03 10:40:57', '2016-07-03 10:40:57', '', 'Rain Garden', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'rain-garden-2', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:41:06', '2016-07-03 10:41:06', '', 438, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Rain-Garden.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(644, 1, '2016-07-03 10:41:16', '2016-07-03 10:41:16', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-643\" src=\"http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Rain-Garden.jpg\" alt=\"Rain Garden\" width=\"870\" height=\"280\" />\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nRain Garden is an important tool to address the environmental concerns raised in the wake of increased stormwater runoff due to urbanization which causes flooding, sweeps away pollutants and have negative repercussions on stormwater treatment.\r\n\r\nRain Garden facilitates soaking of more than 30 % water as compared to the traditional lawns. It checks flooding and drainage. It adds to the beauty of your property.\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>It is not a breeding ground for mosquitoes like lawns without proper stormwater drainage system in place – it attracts birds and dragon flies, the mosquito eaters, instead.</li>\r\n 	<li>No maintenance hassles – occasional weeding and watering will suffice</li>\r\n</ul>', 'Rain Garden', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '438-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:41:16', '2016-07-03 10:41:16', '', 438, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/438-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(645, 1, '2016-07-03 10:42:37', '2016-07-03 10:42:37', '', 'Drainage Doctor', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'drainage-doctor-2', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:42:46', '2016-07-03 10:42:46', '', 442, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drainage-Doctor.jpg', 0, 'attachment', 'image/jpeg', 0),
(646, 1, '2016-07-03 10:42:55', '2016-07-03 10:42:55', '<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-645\" src=\"http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/Drainage-Doctor.jpg\" alt=\"Drainage Doctor\" width=\"870\" height=\"280\" />\r\n\r\n<hr />\r\n\r\nWe also provide commercial and residential drainage system services. We install gutters, repair them, clean them and fix any damages arising from clogged gutters.\r\n\r\nWe also inspect to take preventative measures to save your house\'s drywall, basement, foundation, fascia, soffits, and roof and the gutter themselves.', 'Drainage Doctor', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '442-revision-v1', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:42:55', '2016-07-03 10:42:55', '', 442, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/442-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
