(659, 1, '2016-07-03 10:54:52', '2016-07-03 10:54:52', '<blockquote>\"Mahesh was very responsive, knowledgeable and helpful in determining what I needed done and had his crew there on-time and completed all agreed to services. Mahesh and his crew did a great job! They were able to very successfully \"recover\" several areas of my lawn that had once been landscaped, but become so overgrown you couldn\'t see the plants. Several hours of weeding, trimming and a truck load of mulch later the landscaping and lawn looked great. I\'m planning to use them again for areas of new landscaping and annual lawn maitenance.\"\n\nLaura Gentile</blockquote>\n[gallery link=\"file\" ids=\"660,661,662\"]', 'WalkWay', 'Mahesh was very responsive, knowledgeable and helpful in determining what I needed done and had his crew there on-time and completed all agreed to services. -Laura Gentile', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '239-autosave-v1', '', '', '2016-07-03 10:54:52', '2016-07-03 10:54:52', '', 239, 'http://ecolawnlandscaping.com/239-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
